<HEADLINE> Marino Taken Out With Hurt Shoulder </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	FOXBORO, Mass. (AP) -- Miami's Dan Marino, who has thrown for  
more yards than any quarterback in NFL history, left because of a 
shoulder injury after two series against the New England Patriots 
on Sunday. 
</P>
